supportArticles.title: How to change notification preferences
supportArticles.content: Go to Settings > Notifications to toggle Email and Push alerts for maintenance, payments, and documents.

supportArticles.title: How to configure tenant portal access
supportArticles.content: In Settings > Properties, you can toggle permissions for what tenants can see, such as payment history and document uploads.

supportArticles.title: How rent reminders work
supportArticles.content: Automated reminders are sent 3 days before the due date, on the due date, and every 2 days if the rent remains unpaid.
